</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3047098" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">背景：<a href="http://finance.qq.com/a/20141219/058159.htm?tu_biz=1.114.2.3" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">广东高院判加多宝停用红罐并赔广药1.5亿<i class="icon-external"></i></a><br>加多宝和广药的恩怨渊源不赘述。但问：如何评价此判决？作为加多宝，未来怎么办？</div>


